text:
My slipper... It broke,
and it's hard to walk...

Really... The toe is flapping...
Should I sew it up for you?
It's dangerous like this... That would be better.
I'll go buy a new pair.
Yeah, it would be a disaster if you fell.

Tenka-chan, could you sit on the sofa?
I'll be quick.
Hehe, you're someone we can rely on.

Yeah, I think there are some in the
storage room. I'll go get them.

I was just about to head out anyway.
I'll grab them quickly. Chiyuki, you can relax.
